{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb51ffbf4-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s454"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"454"},"text":"§ 454.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Future Years Homeland Security Program","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb51ffbf5-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s454/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Each budget request submitted to Congress for the Department under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t31/s1105"},"text":"section 1105 of title 31","children":[],"tail":" shall, at or about the same time, be accompanied by a Future Years Homeland Security Program."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb51ffbf6-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s454/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Contents","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Future Years Homeland Security Program under subsection (a) shall—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb51ffbf7-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s454/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" include the same type of information, organizational structure, and level of detail as the future years defense program submitted to Congress by the Secretary of Defense under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s221"},"text":"section 221 of title 10","children":[],"tail":";"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb51ffbf8-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s454/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" set forth the homeland security strategy of the Department, which shall be developed and updated as appropriate annually by the Secretary, that was used to develop program planning guidance for the Future Years Homeland Security Program; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb51ffbf9-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s454/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" include an explanation of how the resource allocations included in the Future Years Homeland Security Program correlate to the homeland security strategy set forth under paragraph (2).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb51ffbfa-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s454/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Effective date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This section shall take effect with respect to the preparation and submission of the fiscal year 2005 budget request for the Department and for any subsequent fiscal year, except that the first Future Years Homeland Security Program shall be submitted not later than 90 days after the Department’s fiscal year 2005 budget request is submitted to Congress.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idb51ffbfb-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/296/tVIII/s874"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–296, title VIII, § 874","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-11-25"},"text":"Nov. 25, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/116/2244"},"text":"116 Stat. 2244","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/330/s5"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–330, § 5","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2004-10-16"},"text":"Oct. 16, 2004","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/118/1278"},"text":"118 Stat. 1278","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idb51ffbfc-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idb51ffbfd-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idb51ffbfe-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2004—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/330"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–330","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (b) and struck out heading and text of former subsec. (b). Text read as follows: “The Future Years Homeland Security Program under subsection (a) of this section shall be structured, and include the same type of information and level of detail, as the Future Years Defense Program submitted to Congress by the Department of Defense under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s221"},"text":"section 221 of title 10","children":[],"tail":".”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idb51ffbff-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"idb51ffc00-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Administrative Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/141/dF/tI/s101"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–141, div. F, title I, § 101","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-03-23"},"text":"Mar. 23, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/606"},"text":"132 Stat. 606","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/115/141/dF/tI/s101"},"text":"“Hereafter, the Secretary of Homeland Security shall submit to the Committees on Appropriations of the Senate and the House of Representatives, at the time the President’s budget proposal is submitted pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t31/s1105/a"},"text":"section 1105(a) of title 31","children":[],"tail":", United States Code, the Future Years Homeland Security Program, as authorized by section 874 of the Homeland Security Act of 2002 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t6/s454"},"text":"6 U.S.C. 454","children":[],"tail":").”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
